title: My car : my place
creator_credit: Bridget Nicholson, ACMI Digital Storytelling and ACMI
brief_description: Bridget Nicholson’s car represents many things to her. More than a way to get from A to B, her car is a private place, a safe place and has intensified the freedom of travel. This Digital Storytelling project was created in partnership with Arts Victoria and the Community Support Fund.
